      },
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "Your Day to Day",
  },
  {
    description: [
      {
        title:
          "You’ll be working directly with the Managing Partner of Moken, as well as in some cases a whole group of startup founders and superstars who are next up for changing the world;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll work in a fast paced environment where no two days are alike;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "Engage our customer throughout the customer journey, with considered Marketing at all\n" +
          "stages;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll elevate the client experience and position Moken as a world-class retailer online;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title: `You’ll identify new opportunities and potential products or ideas to integrate into our offerings;`,
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title: `You’ll ensure an elevated and optimized journey throughout our website;`,
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title: `You’llbBuild and lead the execution of Moken’s eCommerce initiatives to support the
company's overall online sales, brand and customer experience goals;`,
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title: `You’ll drive exceptional conversion metrics through all digital touch points while
ensuring brand experience is consistent on our website(s);`,
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title: `You will be the liaison overseeing any partners managing all 3rd party marketplaces
like Amazon or our internal digital platforms, relaying our brand standards and
reporting on revenue from these platforms;`,
