      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll expertly merchandise our online presence through the analysis of customer\n" +
          "behavior and inventory management;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll strategically plan, execute and monitor 1 to 1 digital channel content via email,\n" +
          "SMS, and other mediums;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You will work closely with product and design teams to develop direct-to-consumer\n" +
          "product exclusives while also using analytics to help guide future product development;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll drive strategy, planning and execution of key acquisition/retargeting channels (email, paid acquisition, SEO/SEM, etc.), to drive engagement and conversion, while tracking against key metrics;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You will analyze site metrics and synthesize digital campaign performance across marketing channels leveraging that information to help lead our customer engagement strategy;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You will lead site experience improvements through analytics, A/B testing and UI/UX research to drive increased conversion and AOV, while also providing a strong user experience that drives satisfaction;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll oversee third party vendors and work with partners on strategic initiatives that will improve site KPIs including product reviews and test/targeting;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You’ll support the preparation of the annual budget, monthly and quarterly forecasts, and monitor reports on results versus budget/forecast based on historical data and analytics.",
        withDash: true

