      {
        title:
          "You’ve got a commitment to quality and investing in results that add value and drive\n" +
          "the business;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You exude the sense of urgency executing job responsibilities, prioritizing urgent and\n" +
          "important work;",
        withDash: true

      },
      {
        title:
          "You have or are actively developing the ability to identify, evaluate, and suggest\n" +
          "business opportunities for today and tomorrow, considering top line and bottom line impacts",
